---
---

<section class="hero-section">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="hero-badge-container">
        <span class="hero-badge">EXPERTISE × AUTONOMY</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="hero-title">
        30年のディレクション経験と、<br />
        自律型AIエージェントの同期。
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-lead">
        AIの速度低下・コード破壊・文脈喪失を克服する。<br />
        公式ガイドにはない、実戦知能の体系。
      </p>

      <div class="hero-points">
        <ul class="points-list">
          <li class="point-item">
            <span class="point-icon"></span>
            30年のキャリアに基づく「判断」を、AIで加速させる技術
          </li>
          <li class="point-item">
            <span class="point-icon"></span>
            実戦投入から抽出された、エラー解決と品質担保のプロトコル
          </li>
          <li class="point-item">
            <span class="point-icon"></span>
            AIに「文脈」を完全に同期させ、思考のズレを排除する管理術
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="#onboarding-panel" class="btn-primary-vibe">
          <span class="btn-text">EXPLORE KNOWLEDGE</span>
          <span class="btn-arrow">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-section {
    padding: 140px 0 100px;
    background: #fff;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .hero-inner {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 100px 60px;
    background: #fff;
    position: relative;
  }

  /* 1pxの緊張感：四隅の極細ボーダー */
  .hero-inner::before, .hero-inner::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hero-inner::before { top: 0; left: 0; border-right: none; border-bottom: none; }
  .hero-inner::after { bottom: 0; right: 0; border-left: none; border-top: none; }

  .hero-badge-container {
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.5em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #000;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    padding: 8px 24px;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .hero-content {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 850px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 3.2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.25;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: #000;
  }

  .hero-lead {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #666;
    line-height: 2;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .hero-points {
    text-align: left;
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
    padding: 40px;
    background: #fafafa;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
  }

  .points-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .point-item {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #333;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .point-item:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  .point-icon {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background: #000;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .btn-primary-vibe {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 20px;
    padding: 24px 60px;
    background: #000;
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    transition: all 0.5s var(--ease-out-expo);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .btn-primary-vibe:hover {
    background: #222;
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .btn-arrow {
    transition: transform 0.4s var(--ease-out-expo);
  }

  .btn-primary-vibe:hover .btn-arrow {
    transform: translateX(10px);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
    .hero-lead {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    .hero-inner {
      padding: 60px 24px;
    }
    .hero-points {
        padding: 30px 20px;
    }
    .btn-primary-vibe {
        width: 100%;
        justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>

